bio:
Legate Sevan Telendas Legate Sevan Telendas is a Dunmer member of the Imperial Legion.
The Dunmer Legate is in command of the Imperial soldiers at the Winterhold Imperial Camp, and if Winterhold is conquered by the Empire during the Civil War, he will replace Kai Wet-Pommel in the Jarl's Longhouse in the city of Winterhold.
name: Legate Sevan Telendas
